ReportDescription: CHange between 4 key etiologies and have a variable that shows up on both landing page and specific wound type.

11.Name: age_distribution
11.SqlCommand:
WITH AgeBuckets AS ( 
    SELECT '0-9' AS AgeBucket, 0 AS MinAge, 9 AS MaxAge
    UNION ALL SELECT '10-19', 10, 19
    UNION ALL SELECT '20-29', 20, 29
    UNION ALL SELECT '30-39', 30, 39
    UNION ALL SELECT '40-49', 40, 49
    UNION ALL SELECT '50-59', 50, 59
    UNION ALL SELECT '60-69', 60, 69
    UNION ALL SELECT '70-79', 70, 79
    UNION ALL SELECT '80-89', 80, 89
    UNION ALL SELECT '90-99', 90, 99
    UNION ALL SELECT 'after 100', 100, 110
),

MostRecentEtiologies AS (
    SELECT 
        n.value AS PrimaryEtiology,
        n.woundFk,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY n.woundFk ORDER BY n.dimDateFk DESC) AS RowNum
    FROM rpt.Note AS n
    INNER JOIN rpt.AttributeType AS atr ON n.attributeTypeFk = atr.id
    WHERE atr.name = 'Primary Etiology'
AND n.value IN ('Arterial Ulcer', 'Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU', 'Lower Extremity Diabetic Ulcers (LEDU)/Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU)/Diabetic Wounds of the Lower Extremity (DWLE)', 'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)')
),
FilteredEtiologies AS (
    SELECT 
        mre.PrimaryEtiology,
        mre.woundFk
    FROM MostRecentEtiologies mre
    WHERE mre.RowNum = 1 -- Only the most recent Primary Etiology per wound
),
Ages AS (
    SELECT 
        fe.PrimaryEtiology,
        fe.woundFk,
        w.patientFk,
        DATEDIFF(YEAR, p.dateOfBirth, GETDATE()) - 
            CASE 
                WHEN MONTH(GETDATE()) < MONTH(p.dateOfBirth) OR 
                     (MONTH(GETDATE()) = MONTH(p.dateOfBirth) AND DAY(GETDATE()) < DAY(p.dateOfBirth)) 
                THEN 1 ELSE 0 
            END AS Age
    FROM FilteredEtiologies AS fe
    INNER JOIN rpt.Wound AS w ON w.id = fe.woundFk
    INNER JOIN rpt.Patient AS p ON w.patientFk = p.id
),
AgeCounts AS (
    SELECT 
        PrimaryEtiology,
        CASE 
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 0 AND 9 THEN '0-9'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 10 AND 19 THEN '10-19'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 20 AND 29 THEN '20-29'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 30 AND 39 THEN '30-39'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 40 AND 49 THEN '40-49'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 50 AND 59 THEN '50-59'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 60 AND 69 THEN '60-69'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 70 AND 79 THEN '70-79'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 80 AND 89 THEN '80-89'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 90 AND 99 THEN '90-99'
            ELSE 'after 100' 
        END AS AgeBucket,
        COUNT(*) AS Count
    FROM Ages
    GROUP BY 
        PrimaryEtiology,
        CASE 
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 0 AND 9 THEN '0-9'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 10 AND 19 THEN '10-19'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 20 AND 29 THEN '20-29'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 30 AND 39 THEN '30-39'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 40 AND 49 THEN '40-49'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 50 AND 59 THEN '50-59'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 60 AND 69 THEN '60-69'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 70 AND 79 THEN '70-79'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 80 AND 89 THEN '80-89'
            WHEN Age BETWEEN 90 AND 99 THEN '90-99'
            ELSE 'after 100' 
        END
),
DistinctPrimaryEtiologies AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT PrimaryEtiology
    FROM Ages
),
AllCombinations AS (
    SELECT 
        ab.AgeBucket,
        ab.MinAge,
        ab.MaxAge,
        pe.PrimaryEtiology
    FROM AgeBuckets AS ab
    CROSS JOIN DistinctPrimaryEtiologies AS pe
)
SELECT 
    ac.PrimaryEtiology,
    ac.AgeBucket,
    COALESCE(ag.Count, 0) AS Count
FROM AllCombinations ac
LEFT JOIN AgeCounts ag 
    ON ac.AgeBucket = ag.AgeBucket AND ac.PrimaryEtiology = ag.PrimaryEtiology
ORDER BY ac.PrimaryEtiology, ac.MinAge;

12.Name: ulcers_with_measurements_improved
12.SqlCommand:
WITH RankedWoundStates AS (
    SELECT 
        n.value AS value,
        n.woundFk AS wound,
        w.patientFk AS patient,
        m.dimDateFk AS minDateFk,
        d.date AS minDate,
        DATEADD(MONTH, 3, d.date) AS maxDate,
        d3.id AS maxDateFk,
        wstt.name AS WoundStateTypeName,
        wst.startDateDimDateFk,
        wst.endDateDimDateFk,
        -- Calculate the absolute difference from the 3-month date
        ABS(d3.id - wst.startDateDimDateFk) AS StartDiff,
        ABS(d3.id - wst.endDateDimDateFk) AS EndDiff,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY n.woundFk 
            ORDER BY 
                ABS(d3.id - wst.startDateDimDateFk) + ABS(d3.id - wst.endDateDimDateFk) ASC
        ) AS RowNum
    FROM rpt.Note AS n
    INNER JOIN rpt.AttributeType AS atr ON n.attributeTypeFk = atr.id
    INNER JOIN rpt.Wound AS w ON w.id = n.woundFk
    INNER JOIN rpt.Patient AS p ON w.patientFk = p.id
    INNER JOIN rpt.Measurement AS m ON m.woundFk = w.id
    INNER JOIN rpt.DimDate AS d ON m.dimDateFk = d.id
    LEFT JOIN rpt.DimDate AS d3 ON d3.date = DATEADD(MONTH, 3, d.date)
    LEFT JOIN rpt.WoundState AS wst 
        ON wst.woundFk = w.id 
       AND (d3.id BETWEEN wst.startDateDimDateFk AND wst.endDateDimDateFk 
            OR (wst.isCurrentState = 1 AND wst.startDateDimDateFk <= d3.id))
    LEFT JOIN rpt.WoundStateType AS wstt ON wstt.id = wst.woundstatetypeFk
    WHERE atr.name = 'Primary Etiology' 
      AND n.dimDateFk = (
          SELECT MAX(n2.dimDateFk)
          FROM rpt.Note AS n2
          INNER JOIN rpt.AttributeType AS atr2 ON n2.attributeTypeFk = atr2.id
          WHERE n2.woundFk = n.woundFk
            AND atr2.name = 'Primary Etiology'
AND n2.value IN ('Arterial Ulcer', 'Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU', 'Lower Extremity Diabetic Ulcers (LEDU)/Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU)/Diabetic Wounds of the Lower Extremity (DWLE)', 'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)')
      )
)
,
InitialAssessmentCTE AS (
    -- Find the earliest assessment date for each woundFk and dimDateFk
    SELECT 
        a.woundFk,
        MIN(a.date) AS earliestAssessmentDate,  -- Get the earliest date
        a.id AS assessmentId,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY a.woundFk ORDER BY MIN(a.date) ASC) AS RowNum -- Rank assessments by date
    FROM rpt.Assessment AS a
    INNER JOIN RankedWoundStates AS rws 
        ON a.woundFk = rws.wound
       AND a.dimDateFk = rws.minDateFk -- Match the initial date
    GROUP BY a.woundFk, a.id
),
ClosestMeasurement AS (
    -- Rank measurements within the range based on proximity to maxDateFk
    SELECT 
        m.woundFk,
        m.volume,
        m.dimDateFk,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY m.woundFk 
            ORDER BY ABS(m.dimDateFk - rws.maxDateFk) ASC
        ) AS MeasurementRank
    FROM rpt.Measurement AS m
    INNER JOIN RankedWoundStates AS rws 
        ON m.woundFk = rws.wound 
       AND m.dimDateFk BETWEEN rws.startDateDimDateFk-21 AND rws.endDateDimDateFk+21
)
SELECT DISTINCT
    rws.value,
    rws.wound,
    rws.patient,
    rws.minDateFk,
    rws.minDate,
    rws.maxDate,
    rws.maxDateFk,
    rws.WoundStateTypeName,
    rws.startDateDimDateFk,
    rws.endDateDimDateFk,
    im.volume AS initialMeasurement, -- Initial measurement with earliest assessment date
    cm.volume AS closestMeasurement, -- Closest measurement to maxDateFk
    cm.dimDateFk AS closestMeasurementDate,
    -- Calculate the percentage change (final/initial * 100)
    CASE 
        WHEN im.volume > 0 THEN (cm.volume / im.volume ) * 100
        ELSE 0
    END AS percentChange,
    -- Bucket the percentages into 0-50%, 50-100%, and 100+
    CASE
        WHEN (cm.volume / im.volume ) * 100 <= 50 THEN 'Decreased by > 50%'
        WHEN (cm.volume / im.volume ) * 100 > 50 AND (cm.volume / im.volume ) * 100 <= 100 THEN 'Decreased by < 50%'
        WHEN (cm.volume / im.volume ) * 100 > 100 THEN 'Increased'
        ELSE 'Unknown'
    END AS percentBucket
FROM RankedWoundStates AS rws
LEFT JOIN InitialAssessmentCTE AS ia 
    ON ia.woundFk = rws.wound -- Join to get the earliest assessment
    AND ia.RowNum = 1 -- Select only the first ranked assessment (earliest)
LEFT JOIN rpt.Measurement AS im 
    ON im.assessmentFk = ia.assessmentId -- Link measurement via assessmentFk
LEFT JOIN ClosestMeasurement AS cm 
    ON cm.woundFk = rws.wound 
   AND cm.MeasurementRank = 1 -- Closest measurement to maxDateFk
WHERE rws.RowNum = 1 -- Only include the closest wound state
  AND WoundStateTypeName = 'open'
  AND im.volume IS NOT NULL  -- Ensure initial measurement exists
  AND cm.volume IS NOT NULL  -- Ensure closest measurement exists
ORDER BY rws.wound;

13.Name: 3month_state
13.SqlCommand:
--gets all woundFk's with most recent primary etiology as arterial ulcer
WITH MostRecentEtiologies AS (
    SELECT 
        n.value AS PrimaryEtiology,
        n.woundFk,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY n.woundFk ORDER BY n.dimdatefk DESC) AS RowNum
    FROM rpt.Note AS n
    INNER JOIN rpt.AttributeType AS atr ON n.attributeTypeFk = atr.id
    WHERE atr.name = 'Primary Etiology'
AND n.value IN ('Arterial Ulcer', 'Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU', 'Lower Extremity Diabetic Ulcers (LEDU)/Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU)/Diabetic Wounds of the Lower Extremity (DWLE)', 'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)')
),


RankedWoundStates AS (
    SELECT 
        mre.PrimaryEtiology,          -- Most recent primary etiology
        mre.woundFk AS wound,
        a.dimDateFk AS minDateFk,     -- Minimum date from the assessment table
        d.date AS minDate,            -- Actual date for the minimum dimDateFk
        DATEADD(MONTH, 3, d.date) AS maxDate, -- 3 months after the minimum date
        d3.id AS maxDateFk,           -- dimDateFk for the maxDate
        wstt.name AS WoundStateTypeName,
        wst.startDateDimDateFk,
        wst.endDateDimDateFk,
        wst.isCurrentState,           -- Indicates if the wound state is the current one
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY mre.woundFk 
            ORDER BY 
                ABS(d3.id - wst.startDateDimDateFk) + ABS(d3.id - wst.endDateDimDateFk) ASC
        ) AS RowNum
    FROM MostRecentEtiologies AS mre
    INNER JOIN rpt.Wound AS w ON w.id = mre.woundFk
    INNER JOIN rpt.Assessment AS a ON w.id = a.woundFk 
    INNER JOIN rpt.AssessmentTypeVersion AS atv ON a.assessmentTypeVersionFk = atv.id 
    INNER JOIN rpt.DimDate AS d ON a.dimDateFk = d.id 
    LEFT JOIN rpt.DimDate AS d3 ON d3.date = DATEADD(MONTH, 3, d.date)
    LEFT JOIN rpt.WoundState AS wst 
        ON wst.woundFk = w.id 
       AND (d3.id BETWEEN wst.startDateDimDateFk AND wst.endDateDimDateFk 
            OR (wst.isCurrentState = 1 AND wst.startDateDimDateFk <= d3.id))
    LEFT JOIN rpt.WoundStateType AS wstt ON wstt.id = wst.woundstatetypeFk
    WHERE mre.RowNum = 1
      AND atv.name = 'Wound Assessment' 
      AND a.dimDateFk = (
          SELECT MIN(a2.dimDateFk)
          FROM rpt.Assessment AS a2
          INNER JOIN rpt.AssessmentTypeVersion AS atv2 ON a2.assessmentTypeVersionFk = atv2.id
          WHERE a2.woundFk = w.id AND atv2.name = 'Wound Assessment'
      )
)

--SELECT * from RankedWoundStates rws ORDER BY rws.wound;

SELECT 
    PrimaryEtiology,       -- Most recent primary etiology
    wound,
    minDateFk,
    minDate,
    maxDate,
    maxDateFk,
    ISNULL(WoundStateTypeName, 'Other') AS WoundStateTypeName, -- Replace NULL with 'Other'
    startDateDimDateFk,
    endDateDimDateFk
FROM RankedWoundStates
WHERE 
    RowNum = 1  -- Only include the closest wound state
    -- Exclude cases where the wound state is current, open, and > 3 weeks from the 3-month date
    AND NOT (
        WoundStateTypeName = 'Open'
        AND isCurrentState = 1
        AND maxDateFk - startDateDimDateFk > 21
    )
ORDER BY minDateFk;

14.Name: healed_wounds
14.SqlCommand:
WITH InitialAssessment AS (
    SELECT 
        a.woundFk AS woundId,
        MIN(a.dimDateFk) AS initialAssessmentDimDateFk,
        MIN(d.date) AS initialAssessmentDate
    FROM rpt.Assessment AS a
    INNER JOIN rpt.DimDate AS d ON a.dimDateFk = d.id
    GROUP BY a.woundFk
),
HealedWounds AS (
    SELECT 
        w.id AS woundId,
        wst.startDateDimDateFk AS healedDateDimDateFk,
        d.date AS healedDate
    FROM rpt.Wound AS w
    INNER JOIN rpt.WoundState AS wst ON w.id = wst.woundFk
    INNER JOIN rpt.WoundStateType AS wstt ON wst.woundstatetypeFk = wstt.id
    LEFT JOIN rpt.DimDate AS d ON wst.startDateDimDateFk = d.id
    WHERE wst.isCurrentState = 1
      AND wstt.name <> 'open'
),
MostRecentEtiologies AS (
    SELECT 
        n.woundFk AS woundId,
        n.value AS primaryEtiology,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY n.woundFk ORDER BY n.dimDateFk DESC) AS RowNum
    FROM rpt.Note AS n
    INNER JOIN rpt.AttributeType AS atr ON n.attributeTypeFk = atr.id
    WHERE atr.name = 'Primary Etiology'
AND n.value IN ('Arterial Ulcer', 'Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU', 'Lower Extremity Diabetic Ulcers (LEDU)/Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU)/Diabetic Wounds of the Lower Extremity (DWLE)', 'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)')
),
PrimaryEtiology AS (
    SELECT
        mre.woundId,
        ISNULL(mre.primaryEtiology, 'Unknown') AS primaryEtiology
    FROM MostRecentEtiologies AS mre
    WHERE mre.RowNum = 1  -- Get only the most recent etiology for each wound
)
SELECT 
    hw.woundId,
    ia.initialAssessmentDate,
    hw.healedDate,
    DATEADD(MONTH, 3, ia.initialAssessmentDate) AS threeMonthsAfterAssessment,
    CASE 
        WHEN hw.healedDate <= DATEADD(MONTH, 3, ia.initialAssessmentDate) THEN 'Before 3 months'
        WHEN hw.healedDate > DATEADD(MONTH, 3, ia.initialAssessmentDate) THEN 'After 3 months'
    END AS StateComparison,
    ISNULL(pe.primaryEtiology, 'Unknown') AS primaryEtiology  -- Ensuring the primary etiology shows as 'Unknown' if no value exists
FROM HealedWounds AS hw
LEFT JOIN InitialAssessment AS ia ON hw.woundId = ia.woundId
INNER JOIN PrimaryEtiology AS pe ON hw.woundId = pe.woundId
ORDER BY hw.woundId;

15.Name: open_wounds_time
15.SqlCommand:
--Gets all CURRENT open wounds 
WITH OpenWounds AS (
    SELECT 
        w.id AS woundId,
        wst.startDateDimDateFk AS startDateDimDateFk,
        d.date AS startDate
    FROM rpt.Wound AS w
    INNER JOIN rpt.WoundState AS wst ON w.id = wst.woundFk
    INNER JOIN rpt.WoundStateType AS wstt ON wst.woundStateTypeFk = wstt.id
    INNER JOIN rpt.DimDate AS d ON wst.startDateDimDateFk = d.id
    WHERE wst.isCurrentState = 1
      AND wstt.name = 'open'
),

--Gets the woundFk's with a primary etiology of arterial ulcer at any given time
MostRecentEtiologies AS (
    SELECT 
        n.woundFk AS woundId,
        n.value AS primaryEtiology,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY n.woundFk ORDER BY n.dimDateFk DESC) AS RowNum
    FROM rpt.Note AS n
    INNER JOIN rpt.AttributeType AS atr ON n.attributeTypeFk = atr.id
    WHERE atr.name = 'Primary Etiology'
AND n.value IN ('Arterial Ulcer', 'Venous Leg Ulcer/VLU', 'Lower Extremity Diabetic Ulcers (LEDU)/Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU)/Diabetic Wounds of the Lower Extremity (DWLE)', 'Pressure Ulcer (PU)/Pressure Injury (PI)')
),

--Gets the woundFk's with most recent primary etiology as arterial ulcer
PrimaryEtiology AS (
    SELECT
        mre.woundId,
        mre.primaryEtiology AS primaryEtiology
    FROM MostRecentEtiologies AS mre
    WHERE mre.RowNum = 1
),

--Gets the difference between the startdate of the 'open' wound state and the current date as months open for all wounds that have a current state of open
WoundDurations AS (
    SELECT 
        ow.woundId,
        ow.startDate,
        DATEDIFF(MONTH, ow.startDate, GETDATE()) AS monthsOpen
    FROM OpenWounds AS ow
)

SELECT 
    wd.woundId,
    wd.startDate,
    wd.monthsOpen,
    CASE
        WHEN wd.monthsOpen BETWEEN 0 AND 3 THEN '0-3 months'
        WHEN wd.monthsOpen BETWEEN 4 AND 6 THEN '3-6 months'
        WHEN wd.monthsOpen BETWEEN 7 AND 9 THEN '6-9 months'
        WHEN wd.monthsOpen BETWEEN 10 AND 12 THEN '9-12 months'
        ELSE 'Over a year'
    END AS timeBracket,
    pe.primaryEtiology
FROM WoundDurations AS wd
INNER JOIN PrimaryEtiology AS pe 
    ON wd.woundId = pe.woundId
ORDER BY timeBracket, wd.woundId;
